The paper discusses the use of machine learning in various domains such as knowledge discovery, natural language processing, information retrieval, and computer vision, which are all covered by the arXiv sub-categories cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.IR, and cs.CV. The paper specifically focuses on how to use world knowledge to enhance machine learning processes, which is a common topic in these sub-categories. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
